quote&gt;&lt;font class=&quot;small&quot;&gt;Quote:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;So, I reinoculated my jars win 1 cc each of spore solution.&amp;nbsp; This time, I didn't shake my jars.&amp;nbsp; The bad part?&amp;nbsp; I did it while I was on mushrooms.&amp;nbsp; I didn't wear a mask or gloves or anything.&amp;nbsp; I did flame the needle each time, but I should have worn a respirator, but I was too far gone to care.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;font class=&quot;post&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:192px;height:auto;&quot; src=&quot;https://files.shroomery.org/smileys/facepalm.gif&quot; alt=&quot;:facepalm:&quot; title=&quot;:facepalm:&quot;/&gt;&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>15100360</next>\n<prev>15099787</prev>\n<first>15086477</first>\n<last>15142196</last>\n<when>1316442232</when>\n<utime>09/19/11 05:23 PM</utime>\n</post>"}